        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'First... I must offer you my apologies.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Why are you apologizing?', 3: '9', 4: 'It\\'s okay.', 5: '10'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": 11,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'For the... \"failed experiments\" I made you eat. I should have known that there was more to food than its appearance.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": 11,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Thank you, Commandant. I knew you would not hold it against me.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Please don\\'t take this the wrong way, but... watching you faint made me realize a great many things about myself.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Not just the old me, but the new me, as well.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'The new you?', 3: '13', 4: 'Have you processed all your memories?', 5: '14'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": 15,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I had my doubts, but they won\\'t be a problem anymore.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": 15,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Not all of it, but the rest won\\'t be a problem.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'A lot of people have been turning up, looking for you for various reasons, Commandant. But I sent them all away.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Nothing important, I hope?', 3: '16', 4: 'Why didn\\'t you wake me?', 5: '17'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": 18,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Some important, some less so. But I took care of them all promptly.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": 18,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Because the exhaustion must be piling up for you, what with our recent missions and... incidents. I took the liberty of safeguarding your rest.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'There are no missions scheduled today, so you can rest easy. I will take watch.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kind of hard to fall asleep with someone watching.', 3: '19', 4: 'Shouldn\\'t you go get some rest too?', 5: '20'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": 21,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Is that so... I can turn away—I guess that wouldn\\'t help any.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": 21,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Taking watch is rest enough for me, Commandant.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'What\\'s with that expression...? We\\'ve been together like this for long, Commandant, even if I wasn\\'t always privy to your condition...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'According to the records, you were the one person whom I have been with the longest. I am simply adhering to my past behavior.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'So... in short.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '6'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I would like to share our time together, Commandant.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Whoa...', 3: '25', 4: 'If that\\'s what you\\'d like...', 5: '25'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'No, please don\\'t answer. I did not express my feelings to elicit a reply.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'As she speaks, Lucia presents you with a paper crane. It\\'s been carefully folded countless times, and you can faintly make out scribbles in between the creases.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'From the scribbles, you make out a set of groundside coordinates, close to the new HQ you set up together, and these words: \"I hope that you\\'ll be there, at the appointed time.\"'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": 1,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Simply put... I\\'m asking you out on a date.', 4: '1'}"
